{"id":870,"parent_id":828,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":870,"title":"Ezekiel 42","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ezek.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 42"],[".studySummary",["i","Ezekiel sees in the temple the chambers for the priests."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.1","order":"02.27.042.58275"},["b","1"],"Then he brought me forth into the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"utter court"],", the way toward the north: and he brought me into the chamber that",["i","was"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"over against"],"the separate place, and which",["i","was"],"before the building toward the north."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.2","order":"02.27.042.58276"},["b","2"],"Before the length of an hundred cubits",["i","was"],"the north door, and the breadth",["i","was"],"fifty cubits."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.3","order":"02.27.042.58277"},["b","3"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Over against"],"the twenty",["i","cubits"],"which",["i","were"],"for the inner court, and over against the pavement which",["i","was"],"for the utter court,",["i","was"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"gallery"],"against gallery in three",["i","stories."]],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.4","order":"02.27.042.58278"},["b","4"],"And before the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"chambers"],["i","was"],"a walk of ten cubits breadth inward, a way of one cubit; and their doors toward the north."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.5","order":"02.27.042.58279"},["b","5"],"Now the upper chambers",["i","were"],"shorter: for the galleries were higher than these, than the lower, and than the middlemost of the building."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.6","order":"02.27.042.58280"},["b","6"],"For they",["i","were"],"in three",["i","stories,"],"but had not pillars as the pillars of the courts: therefore",["i","the building"],"was straitened more than the lowest and the middlemost from the ground."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.7","order":"02.27.042.58281"},["b","7"],"And the wall that",["i","was"],"without over against the chambers, toward the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"utter"],"court on the forepart of the chambers, the length thereof",["i","was"],"fifty cubits."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.8","order":"02.27.042.58282"},["b","8"],"For the length of the chambers that",["i","were"],"in the utter court",["i","was"],"fifty cubits: and, lo, before the temple",["i","were"],"an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"hundred"],"cubits."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.9","order":"02.27.042.58283"},["b","9"],"And from under these chambers",["i","was"],"the entry on the east side, as one goeth into them from the utter court."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.10","order":"02.27.042.58284"},["b","10"],"The chambers",["i","were"],"in the thickness of the wall of the court toward the east, over against the separate place, and over against the building."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.11","order":"02.27.042.58285"},["b","11"],"And the way before them",["i","was"],"like the appearance of the chambers which",["i","were"],"toward the north, as long as they,",["i","and"],"as broad as they: and all their goings out",["i","were"],"both according to their fashions, and according to their doors."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.12","order":"02.27.042.58286"},["b","12"],"And according to the doors of the chambers that",["i","were"],"toward the south",["i","was"],"a door in the head of the way,",["i","even"],"the way directly before the wall toward the east, as one entereth into them."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.13","order":"02.27.042.58287"},["b","13"],"¶Then said he unto me, The north chambers",["i","and"],"the south chambers, which",["i","are"],"before the separate place, they",["i","be"],"holy chambers, where the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"priests"],"that approach unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"eat"],"the most holy things: there shall they lay the most holy things, and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"meat offering"],", and the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_13d"},"sin offering"],", and the trespass offering; for the place",["i","is"],"holy."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.14","order":"02.27.042.58288"},["b","14"],"When the priests enter therein, then shall they not go out of the holy",["i","place"],"into the utter court, but there they shall lay their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"garments"],"wherein they minister; for they",["i","are"],"holy; and shall put on other garments, and shall approach to",["i","those things"],"which",["i","are"],"for the people."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.15","order":"02.27.042.58289"},["b","15"],"Now when he had made an end of measuring the inner house, he brought me forth toward the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"gate"],"whose prospect",["i","is"],"toward the east, and measured it round about."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.16","order":"02.27.042.58290"},["b","16"],"He measured the east side with the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"measuring"],"reed, five hundred reeds, with the measuring reed round about."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.17","order":"02.27.042.58291"},["b","17"],"He measured the north side, five hundred reeds, with the measuring reed round about."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.18","order":"02.27.042.58292"},["b","18"],"He measured the south side, five hundred reeds, with the measuring reed."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.19","order":"02.27.042.58293"},["b","19"],"¶He turned about to the west side,",["i","and"],"measured five hundred reeds with the measuring reed."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.20","order":"02.27.042.58294"},["b","20"],"He",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"measured"],"it by the four sides: it had a wall round about,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"five"],"hundred",["i","reeds"],"long, and five hundred broad, to make a separation between the sanctuary and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"profane"],"place."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.1a","order":"02.27.042.58295"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/40.20"},"Ezek. 40:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.1b","order":"02.27.042.58297"},["b","1b"],["span.small","OR"],"opposite."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.3a","order":"02.27.042.58299"},["b","3a"],["span.small","OR"],"Adjoining."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.3b","order":"02.27.042.58301"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.16.15-16"},"Ezek. 41:16 (15–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.4a","order":"02.27.042.58303"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/40.17"},"Ezek. 40:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.10"},"41:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/46.19"},"46:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.7a","order":"02.27.042.58305"},["b","7a"],["span.small","OR"],"outer."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.8a","order":"02.27.042.58307"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/40.47"},"Ezek. 40:47"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/41.13"},"41:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.13a","order":"02.27.042.58309"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/40.46"},"Ezek. 40:46"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.13b","order":"02.27.042.58311"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/6.26.16,26"},"Lev. 6:26 (16, 26)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/10.13"},"10:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.13c","order":"02.27.042.58313"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/2.1.1,3,10"},"Lev. 2:1 (1, 3, 10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.13d","order":"02.27.042.58315"},["b","13d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/4.3.2-3"},"Lev. 4:3 (2–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/40.39"},"Ezek. 40:39"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.14a","order":"02.27.042.58317"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/44.19"},"Ezek. 44:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.15a","order":"02.27.042.58319"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/40.6"},"Ezek. 40:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/43.1.1-2"},"43:1 (1–2)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/44.1"},"44:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.16a","order":"02.27.042.58321"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/40.3"},"Ezek. 40:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.20a","order":"02.27.042.58323"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/40.5"},"Ezek. 40:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.20b","order":"02.27.042.58325"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/45.2"},"Ezek. 45:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"20c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/42.20c","order":"02.27.042.58327"},["b","20c"],["span.small","OR"],"common.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/45.6"},"Ezek. 45:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/48.15"},"48:15"],"."]]}
